quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  96,10,"fún ẹrúsìn kan nígbà tí (ẹrúsìn náà) kírun!"
  96,11,"Sọ fún mi (nípa ẹ̀san rẹ̀) tí ó bá jẹ́ pé ó wà lórí ìmọ̀nà (’Islām)"
  96,12,"tàbí pé ó pàṣẹ ìbẹ̀rù (Allāhu)!"
  98,4,"Àwọn tí A fún ní tírà kò sì di ìjọ ọ̀tọ̀ọ̀tọ̀ àfi lẹ́yìn tí ẹ̀rí tó yanjú dé bá wọn."
  98,5,"Àwa kò sì pa wọ́n ní àṣẹ kan bí kò ṣe pé kí wọ́n jọ́sìn fún Allāhu lẹ́ni tí yóò máa ṣe àfọ̀mọ́ ẹ̀sìn fún Un,{1} lẹ́ni tí yóò dúró ṣinṣin nínú ẹ̀sìn. Kí wọ́n kírun, kí wọ́n sì yọ Zakāh. Ìyẹn sì ni ẹ̀sìn tó fẹsẹ̀ rinlẹ̀..",footnotes:1:Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah Al-’a‘rọ̄f 7:29.
  98,6,"Dájúdájú àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ (wọ̀nyí) nínú àwọn ahlul-kitāb àti àwọn ọ̀ṣẹbọ, wọn yóò wà nínú Iná. Olùṣegbére ni wọ́n nínú rẹ̀. Àwọn wọ̀nyẹn, àwọn ni ẹ̀dá tó burú jùlọ."
  99,1,"Nígbà tí wọ́n bá mi ilẹ̀ tìtì ní ìmìtìtì rẹ̀,"
  99,2,"àti (nígbà) tí ilẹ̀ bá tú àwọn ẹrù tó wúwo nínú rẹ̀ jáde,"
  99,3,"ènìyàn yó sì wí pé: “Kí l’ó mú un?”"